    "type": "message",
    "text": "Hi folks. I’m Will Crichton, a CS PhD student at Stanford. I work on large-scale programmable systems (e.g. <https://github.com/scanner-research/scanner>) and I also teach the programming languages course here (<http://cs242.stanford.edu/f18/>). Deeply interested in the psychology of programming and understanding cognitive models of computation. Also, of course got a blog: <http://willcrichton.net/notes/>",
